    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>You gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic weapon. The bonus increases to +3 when you use the mace to attack a &amp;Reference[construct]{construct}.</p>\n<p>When you roll a 20 on an attack roll made with this weapon, the target takes an extra 7 &amp;Reference[bludgeoning]{bludgeoning} damage, or 14 &amp;Reference[bludgeoning]{bludgeoning} damage if it's a &amp;Reference[construct]{construct}. If a &amp;Reference[construct]{construct} has 25 hit points or fewer after taking this damage, it is destroyed.</p>\n</div>",
